supposedly able to play for short periods of time and make progress. All the classes are supposed to be able to solo well and down time is supposed to be minimal. <br>
<br>
I think RP opportunities abound. From what I’ve read I liken the world to a cross between Dune and Shadow Run. Funcom the games maker is promising a 4 year on going story line that’s set to start a couple months after release with player actions dictating the story. Which is Corporations ie Omni-tek vs. the Rebel Clans. If you hadn’t heard anything about this game, which I doubt their website can be found here www.anarchyonline.com . The Game has already gone gold and should be on store shelves the 27th of this month one short week away.  <br>
